  <brief_title>Randomized Phase III Study of Folfiri+Avastin Versus Xeliri+Avastin as 1st Line Treatment of CRC</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Phase III Study of Irinotecan Plus 5-fluorouracil Plus Leucovorin and Bevacizumab (FOLFIRI+Avastin) Versus Irinotecan Plus Capecitabine and Bevacizumab (XELIRI+Avastin) as 1st Line Treatment of Locally Advanced or Metastatic Colorectal Cancer</official_title>
